   <p>Herv\u00e9 Pignon<\/p>\n                <p>Directeur &#8211; Hauts-de-France<\/p>\n                            <\/div>          \n        <\/div>\n                <div class=\"interlocuteur__element\">\n            <div class=\"interlocuteur__image\">\n                                <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/territoireengagetransitionecologique.ademe.fr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/Re\u0301fe\u0301rent-Hauts-de-France-cedric-alvera.jpg\" alt=\"C\u00e9dric Alvera\">\n                            <\/div> \n            <div class=\"interlocuteur__texte\">\n                <p>C\u00e9dric Alvera<\/p>\n                <p>R\u00e9f\u00e9rent &#8211; Hauts-de-France<\/p>\n                            <\/div>          \n        <\/div>\n        <\/section>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group is-layout-flow\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-group fond__vert is-layout-flow\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Vous souhaitez rejoindre<br>Territoire Engag\u00e9 Transition \u00c9cologique ?<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\"><strong>Vous souhaitez valoriser votre engagement et l\u2019efficacit\u00e9 de vos politiques en faveur du climat, de la qualit\u00e9 de l\u2019air et des \u00e9conomies d\u2019\u00e9nergie ?<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\">Int\u00e9grez la d\u00e9marche de labellisation Territoire Engag\u00e9 Transition \u00c9cologique,<br>et rejoignez le r\u00e9seau \u00ab European Energy Award (EEA) \u00bb, qui compte \u00e0 ce jour pr\u00e8s de 1 200 collectivit\u00e9s europ\u00e9ennes.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-buttons is-horizontal is-content-justification-center is-layout-flex wp-container-2\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-button citergie__bouton\"><a class=\"wp-block-button__link wp-element-button\" href=\"\/contact\" rel=\"\/contact\">Contact<\/a><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div><\/div>\n<\/div><\/div>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{